---
- Use appropriate error handling for file operations
- Support both relative and absolute paths
- Validate file existence before reading
- Create parent directories when writing to new paths
- Use context managers (with statements) for file handles
- Handle encoding issues gracefully (especially for cross-platform use)
- Implement appropriate backup strategies before overwriting files
